Frequently Asked Questions

Frequently Asked Questions

What is LiFE RPG?

LiFE RPG is a gamified Notion Template that reimagines your life's journey as an immersive role-playing game. Through innovative gamification elements, this system helps you gamify your life, making self-improvement and life goals not just achievable, but genuinely engaging and fun.

What is the IDEA behind LiFE RPG?

The idea behind LiFE RPG is inspired by Yu-kai Chou's Octalysis framework from his book 'Actionable Gamification: Beyond Points, Badges, and Leaderboards.' This insightful resource explores the design and implementation of gamified systems, aiming to enhance user engagement, motivate behavior, and help you achieve your goals through effective gamification strategies.

Do I need to pay for any updates?

No, once you purchase LiFE RPG, you'll receive lifetime updates, even if the price increases in the future.

Do I need to pay for any updates?

Yes! LiFE RPG is a highly customizable Notion template with a high degree of freedom, and tailoring it to match your workflow as much as possible can be beneficial. Once you've completed your purchase, you can customize the the template to perfectly suit your requirements.

Can I get a refund?

Given the inherent characteristics of digital products, all sales are deemed final and non-refundable.

Do I have to pay for the Notion paid plan?

No, this template's design and functionality are compatible with the Notion free plan. You can use our template with a free account.

What are the benefits of paying for Notion templates?

By investing in Notion templates, you save a lot of time and effort of starting from scratch to create complex databases, attributes, layouts, formulas, and dashboards. This simplifies the barrier of entry to using Notion. Previously, using Notion required setting up your own system before getting started. Now, with just a click of a button, you can have a professionally structured and formatted Notion system. This allows you to allocate more time to important tasks, significantly boosting efficiency.

How to use Notion Template?

After purchasing, you will be given a link to the Notion template for LiFE RPG. Clicking on the link will open a Notion page in your browser. To duplicate the template to your Notion workspace, simply locate the "Start with this template" button at the top right of the page. In addition, you will also receive a link to a tutorial on how to use LiFE RPG via email.
